00:18:40.930 --> 00:18:42.100
on the web.

00:18:42.100 --> 00:18:44.647
They also want drive innovative
solutions for their users,

00:18:44.647 --> 00:18:46.980
and they want to go beyond
mobile banking in their apps.

00:18:46.980 --> 00:18:50.740
They want to be able to enable
their cardholders to use

00:18:50.740 --> 00:18:53.134
mobile payments from
their apps, controlling

00:18:53.134 --> 00:18:55.300
the branding experience but
without writing millions

00:18:55.300 --> 00:18:56.520
